theorem Topology.dense_iff_interiorClosure_eq_univ
    {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] {A : Set X} :
    Dense (A : Set X) ↔ interior (closure (A : Set X)) = (Set.univ : Set X) := by
  constructor
  · intro hDense
    simpa using
      (interior_closure_eq_univ_of_dense (A := A) hDense)
  · intro hInt
    -- From `interior (closure A) = univ`, deduce `closure A = univ`.
    have h_univ_subset : (Set.univ : Set X) ⊆ closure (A : Set X) := by
      have h_int_subset :
          interior (closure (A : Set X)) ⊆ closure (A : Set X) :=
        interior_subset
      simpa [hInt] using h_int_subset
    have h_closure_univ :
        closure (A : Set X) = (Set.univ : Set X) := by
      apply Set.Subset.antisymm
      · intro _ _; trivial
      · exact h_univ_subset
    exact ⟨h_closure_univ⟩
